mha4mysql-manager (0.61-0+local1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Normalize read_only values returned by MySQL and MariaDB.
  * Support MariaDB NO_LOCK and NO_LOCK_NO_ADMIN read-only modes.
  * Preserve strict MariaDB read-only modes instead of weakening them.
  * Fail explicitly for undefined or unsupported read_only values.

 -- TalyMeal <furyseer@gmail.com>  Wed, 15 Jul 2026 16:59:49 +0300

mha4mysql-manager (0.60-0+local1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Add the ping_max_failures configuration option for controlling the
    number of consecutive failed master health checks before failover.
  * Keep the existing threshold of four failures as the default for
    backward compatibility.
  * Apply the threshold to connection failures and query ping failures.

 -- TalyMeal <furyseer@gmail.com>  Tue, 14 Jul 2026 02:05:42 +0300

mha4mysql-manager (0.59-0+local1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Add MariaDB GTID replication support for monitoring, failover and
    online master switch.
  * Use MariaDB GTID positions and MASTER_USE_GTID=slave_pos when
    reparenting replicas.
  * Synchronize online switches by MariaDB GTID and report replica IO
    startup errors without waiting for the SQL thread timeout.
  * Require mha4mysql-node 0.59 for compatible MariaDB client and
    raw-binlog handling.

 -- A S <furyseer@gmail.com>  Sun, 12 Jul 2026 14:00:00 +0300

